Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:38.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must fight the towering foe!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:38.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kyodai na teki o
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:41.47,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Fight! Fight! Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:41.47,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uteyo! Uteyo! Uteyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:48.27,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Bring to bear the rage of justice, Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:48.27,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Seigi no ikari o butsukero GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:54.61,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:54.61,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:58.53,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Rise once more! Rise once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:58.53,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Yomigaeru! Yomigaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.66,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Rise once more! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.66,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Yomigaeru GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must seize the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kimi yo tsukame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Fly toward the galaxy, Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Ginga e mukatte tobeyo GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.12,0:01:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Mr. Ryu, standby okay!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.58,0:01:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, standby for docking.\NReady?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going in, Mr. Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.37,0:01:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,5... 4... 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.97,0:01:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,2... 1...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Laser searcher synchronized.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,5... 4...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.29,0:01:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Gundam B Parts released!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.26,0:01:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Core Change! Docking, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.70,0:02:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The youthful crew train\Nas they proceed across Central Asia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.88,0:02:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The endless fighting has not let up\Nsince they left Side 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.61,0:02:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro Deserts
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.81,0:03:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really focused, aren't you?\NSo what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.90,0:03:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm drawing up combat simulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We've learned the Zaku's actual performance\Nfrom the one we captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,By entering those parameters\Nalong with Gundam's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm seeing if I can come up with\Nmore accurate combat patterns.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But... it won't do you any good...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...against the new Gouf mobile suit\Nthat the prisoner talked about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.36,0:03:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I've increased the Zaku's performance\Nby 20% to account for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.75,0:03:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well. That's our Amuro for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.88,0:03:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- Want me to take over?\N- Thanks. I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.76,0:04:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- Please do get some sleep, Amuro.\N- Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.02,0:04:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it going, Bright?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.56,0:04:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Another too-young woman soldier, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.88,0:04:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't accept the fact that\NI'm the commander of this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ensign Cozun Graham...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...where is Ramba Ral's Gallop,\Nor whatever it's called?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,An officer should know\Nhow to treat another officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I've checked the Antarctic Treaty,\NEnsign Cozun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, won't you tell us about M'Quve's mines?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I can't talk that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Water...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! Come fix it! Fix the plumbing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The plumbing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kikka...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...Ms. Mirai's here, right? Ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai! The water!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.61,0:04:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kikka...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:05:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I was doing the laundry,\Nbut now the water won't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, please stay!\NCould you check the faucet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure. I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.18,0:05:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the way, Kikka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kikka, what happened to the handle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in the sink.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.05,0:05:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.43,0:05:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's fixed! It's fixed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.69,0:05:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a lifesaver, Amuro.\NIs it completely fixed now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No...\NI think you need to have it fixed properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.94,0:05:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.66,0:05:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This Zaku has seen a lot of use.\NWill it be all right, Clamp?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The overhaul report looks good, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.17,0:05:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The joints have been replaced\Nwith new ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.13,0:06:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The Fat Uncle may return.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You may leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the Trojan Horse been up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.32,0:06:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why exactly did you accept this mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- Do you disapprove?\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as you think. This is a mission\Nof personal vengeance for the Zabi family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...if I destroy the Trojan Horse\Nand avenge Lord Garma in this battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'll receive a special two-rank promotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.37,0:06:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My promotion would also\Nsecure the livelihoods of my men.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for the men?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll rub shoulders with the Zabis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You just wait and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think you'll get out any time soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.31,0:06:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Amateurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't even do a proper body search.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a Zeon, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want, you can escape with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.59,0:07:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to misunderstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're escaping, I'll call for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.89,0:07:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- What?!\N- Somebody! The prisoner's escaping!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody! Please come!\NThe prisoner is escaping! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.48,0:07:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- Missiles!\N- Fire our missiles horizontally!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.58,0:07:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- Can you tell where they were fired from?\N- From the ground. 11 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.71,0:07:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, M'Quve's got a base this far east.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.14,0:08:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Scope! Maximum magnification!\NExamine the base in front!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.01,0:08:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, launch the Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger. Amuro, launching.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I may have to do a mid-air transfer.right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.11,0:08:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mid-air transfer?\NAmuro! What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.95,0:08:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! Are you sure about this?!\NYou'll get in trouble with Mr. Bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.04,0:08:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'm confident\NI can explain this to Mr. Bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to head out. Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.80,0:08:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The Guntank has launched.\NIt's Hayato and Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What? It's not Ryu? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Bright!re are you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:09:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Sayla just told me! The prisoner's escaped!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll get Sayla to search him out!.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- The Guntank has left.\N- What?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped...\NHunt down that prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot him if you have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.43,0:09:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- I'm counting on you.ll find him somehow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.12,0:09:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Operator, check inside the ship!\NQuickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing that prisoner, I'm sure he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...going to try and contact his comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.35,0:09:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This machine is so hard to tune in!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.19,0:09:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mustang 2, Mustang 2!\NThis is Cozun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Transmitting from the Trojan Horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.71,0:09:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, here you are.\NWe have a message from Cozun, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! From Cozun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There are three types:\NGundam, Guntank, and Guncannon
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Only one of each Is on the Trojan Horse.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:10:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know If they have fighters...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is somebody in the number 2 comm room?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What? There shouldn't be anyone there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The comm circuit is open.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's check the monitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The TV circuit has been cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- Shut off the master comm circuit!\N- Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Piece of junk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Bright. How much information\Ndo you think was leaked?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the enemy in front of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And it looks like he's called in\NRamba Ral's Gouf team, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming in on your right, Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I see 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:11:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Right on, Hayato.\NFor a ground base like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...the firepower and mobility\Nof the Guntank is just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright doesn't really\Nunderstand tactics yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Fighting everything with the Gundam\Nisn't always the best solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.17,0:11:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- Anything from Captain M'Quve?!\N- Yes. He's sent out Dopps to support us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.55,0:11:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been unable to make contact since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what are they thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would they hit a mine like this,\Nwith no strategic value at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.75,0:11:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ensign.\N- What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramba Ral's Gallop is on its way\Nto give us support.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramba Ral?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Garma's revenge team.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.94,0:11:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean... the infamous\NTrojan Horse is attacking our base?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Good, Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a question of time\Nbefore we take down that base.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.88,0:12:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Cozun. You just get out of there safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.55,0:12:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.07,0:12:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He's coming! He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Defense attack! Go, Haro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.75,0:12:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The prisoner's headed for Hatch 18!\NIs anybody there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Dopps! And there's something\Napproaching on the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:13:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be the Gallop the prisoner mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayla can deal with the prisoner somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We need Ryu and Kai!\NAnd Amuro must transfer to the Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.69,0:13:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu! Kai! Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy reinforcements have appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.43,0:13:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! I'm launching!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.82,0:13:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai, in the Guncannon! Now launching!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.50,0:13:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Balance is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.77,0:13:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm landing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see it now. Damn Trojan Horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a Dopp formation,\Nhere to support us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off. I don't like to say things like\N"this time for sure", but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The Trojan Horse has three mobile suits\Nin action. Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.61,0:14:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes me wish we had three Goufs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.28,0:14:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If Cozun escapes, make sure he's rescued.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghien! Stetch! Keep up with me!\NWe're launching!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.18,0:14:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! Dopps! Turn to left!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.69,0:14:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Just five or six Dopps...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Amuro! Do you read?!t?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Retreat, while the Guncannonu!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Transfer to the Gundam!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.66,0:14:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Aim properly, Hayato! These Dopps\Nshouldn't be a problem for the Guntank!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm doing the best I can, but...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.69,0:14:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm fine!ft! Zakus!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakus?! And the new mobile suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:15:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The prisoner called it a Gouf!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.80,0:15:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Hayato! Fire!\N- Roger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.81,0:15:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That Zaku's moving faster than I calculated!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amuro! Return!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We're heading back, Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.68,0:15:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The Guntank's useless against moving foes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai! Do you read?! Cover us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.87,0:15:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! You gotta be kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.11,0:15:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Move the White Base forward!\NIt's too much for just the Guncannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.86,0:15:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mirai, we'll charge with the White Base!\N- Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Port-side! Keep that Gallop away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do you read?!\NWe're opening the hatch! Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.94,0:15:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I have this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:16:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ms. Sayla! Where's the prisoner?!\N- He's in the airlock! He's going to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.57,0:16:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't open it with a sidearm.\NIt's not that cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.95,0:16:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla, step back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Good...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.26,0:16:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't feel guilty.\NIt could be us next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.14,0:16:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.98,0:16:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Control system is transferred!\NStandby to launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! Is the transfer complete?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.70,0:16:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla? Are you allowed there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry, but I have to be here for now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayla. Where's Cozun, the prisoner?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. He's... dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.63,0:17:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,At least we've stopped\Nany further information leaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.51,0:17:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! Provide support for Kai! Hurry!\NCover for White Base is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy's clever!\NThey're spreading out in four directions!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- Which is the strongest?!\N- The new mobile suit in the center, the Gouf!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Gouf... The Gouf, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end for you,\NFederation mobile suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.74,0:17:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.45,0:17:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, launch now.\NPlease take care of the Guncannon in front.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.17,0:17:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.12,0:17:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.81,0:17:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not working!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:18:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The computer's patterns can't keep up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Was the data inaccurate?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.11,0:18:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to cover the Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Concentrate fire only on the Gouf in front!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! The shock wave from the blast\Nscrewed up the joints.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Must I fall back without a fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If only the ground forces had held up better,\Nwe could have managed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.31,0:18:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghien! Stetch! We're retreating!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Return to the Gallop at Point R!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.61,0:18:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to launch in the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.03,0:18:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy was weak, so we survived. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.66,0:18:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fact that the Guntank was\Nthe best choice for attacking a fortress...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:18:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Gallop joined in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A soldier can't predict everything\Nabout an operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Never disobey orders!\NThat's a violation of military regulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.37,0:19:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- Military regulations?!\N- That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a necessity during combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.26,0:19:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...are we regular soldiers now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.57,0:19:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro's thinking hard and\Ndoing the best he can, Bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.77,0:19:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If I just accepted that, we'd all end up dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.69,0:19:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Ryu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose that's logical...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a complete disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.91,0:19:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gouf's and Zaku's movements\Nare completely different...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...depending on environment and pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.37,0:19:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll have to start over\Nfrom the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.31,0:20:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't really agree with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Job can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Omur has done simulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No repairs on the Cannon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The spare arm is being repaired\Nin the workshop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.70,0:20:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. So, what do you think, Mirai?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.41,0:20:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He may be too young,\Nbut that doesn't make him unsuitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.55,0:20:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it would be better if we\Nentrusted Ryu with the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You've already decided, haven't you, Bright?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,To take Amuro off of the Gundam?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.42,0:20:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have enough time\Nto wait for one boy to grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this is no training ground, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.44,0:20:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...maybe we can give Amuro a bit of a rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.90,0:20:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.35,0:20:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro's a special boy.\NI have a strong feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.89,0:20:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai, I want you to agree with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.62,0:21:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.75,0:21:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you heard us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.89,0:21:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's spared us the trouble\Nof explaining it all to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.06,0:21:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.11,0:21:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.99,0:21:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.95,0:21:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.62,0:21:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.99,0:21:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm getting off the ship.\N- What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.91,0:21:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright and Ms. Mirai say\NI'm no longer necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.59,0:21:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I'm leaving the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.09,0:21:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.54,0:22:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.22,0:22:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.52,0:22:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mr. Bright! The Gundam Is launching!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.81,0:22:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come In, Gundam!Gundam!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.11,0:22:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come In!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.44,0:22:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Marker! Can you close the hatch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.69,0:22:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Impossible! Catapult Is launching!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.12,0:22:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.09,0:22:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That Amuro...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.88,0:23:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Alone with the Gundam...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.00,0:23:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...Amuro attacks M'Quve's mining facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.16,0:23:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That is where he sees...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.67,0:23:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...Kycilia, a leader of the Zabi family.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.55,0:23:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Will M'Quve's base be destroyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.63,0:23:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Or will the Adzam melt down the Gundam?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.77,0:23:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam. Next episode...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.05,0:23:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Zeon's Secret Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.72,0:23:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Zeon's Secret Mine
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.06,0:23:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.07,0:23:54.91,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.91,0:23:59.91,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The star shining far off in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:10.13,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, it's your homeland\Nwhere you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.13,0:24:15.05,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the days\Nof your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.05,0:24:19.68,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The morning when you woke up in warmth?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.68,0:24:25.06,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.06,0:24:29.65,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,A man must hide his tears, hide his tears
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.65,0:24:39.95,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Only look to tomorrow, to tomorrow\NForever...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.07,0:23:54.91,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Furimukanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.91,0:23:59.91,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uchuu no kanata ni kagayaku hoshi ha
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:10.13,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Omae no umareta furusato da
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.13,0:24:15.05,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oboeteirukai, Shounen no hi no koto wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.05,0:24:19.68,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Atatakai nukumori no nake de mezameta asa wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.68,0:24:25.06,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, furimukanaide na, Amuro
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.06,0:24:29.65,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Otoko ha namida wo misenu mono, Misenu mono
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.65,0:24:39.95,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tada ashita e to ashita e to, Eien ni...
